page.title: 11Whiteparish-Clubs etc.
page.content: {Playgroup,}Mon.,Tues.,Wed.;{Mothers' {Club.},Fortnightly ;{Baby Fellowship, Thurs.at 2.30;{Mothers' Union,}1st Wed 2.30 and 3rd Tues 7.30;{Prayer Group ; {Choir Practice,}Fri 6.30 ;{Sunday {School,}10am Church ;{Bright Hour,}2nd and 4th Wed,2.30 ;{Friendship Club, 1st and 3rd Mon. 2.30;{Women's {Institute,}3rd Wed,2.30;{Horticultural {Society,}4th Thurs.7.30 ;{Flower Club, 3rd Thurs 7.30 ;{Football Club}; {Cricket Club ; Royal British Legion}; {School - Association ; Youth Club, Wed.(Junior) Fri.(Senior) ;{Badminton {Club,}Mon. Tues. Wed. Thurs.;{Ladies {Keep Fit,}Tues.;{Cubs and Scouts, Tues. (Cubs), Thurs. (Scouts); As will be seen, Whiteparish is a very lively village and therefore clubs tend to vary from year to year. These clubs are in existence at the time of writing.i.e. as at 5/7/85.
